creator: Andrew Lang
description:
LibriVox recording of Tales of Troy: Ulysses the Sacker of Cities by Andrew Lang.
Read in English by Eleanor Howard; Scott Bennett; Kathrine Engan; Larry Wilson; James K. White; Kevin W. Davidson; Maggie Travers
These are short stories about the life of Ulysses, the stealing of Helen, Paris, battles, Trojan horses, and more! - Summary by Maggie Travers
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
